<!-- Original cookie code - v2 -->
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/cookieconsent@3/build/cookieconsent.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/cookieconsent@3/build/cookieconsent.min.js"  data-cfasync="false"></script>

<script>
var gtm_pageHostnameTLD = {{jsv_pageHostnameTLD - Blocked by Blacklisting}};

// Load popup
window.cookieconsent.initialise({
  "palette": {
    "popup": {
      "background": "#fff7bc",
      "text": "#303030"
    },
    "button": {
      "background": "#008067",
      "text": "#ffffff"
    }
  },
  "position": "top",
  "static": true,
  "content": {
    "message": "We use cookies on our website to make your online experience better, tailor messages to you and improve our performance. You can find out more about our cookies by visiting our cookies policy. If you simply continue to browse we’ll assume you’re ok with this.",
    "dismiss": "Accept & Close",
    "link": "Manage Cookies",
    "href": "/cookies-policy#manage-cookies" // main-content
  },
  "cookie": {
    "name": "cookieconsent_status",
    "domain": gtm_pageHostnameTLD
  },
  onStatusChange: function(status) {
      dataLayer.push({
        "eventCategory": "navigation",
        "eventAction": "click: accept and close popup",
        "eventLabel": {{Lookup_allowRemarketing1 - browserDoNotTrack}},
        "eventValue": 0,
        "eventNonInteractive": true,
        "cookieconsent_status": "accepted",
        "event": "gtm_linkClick_acceptCookies"
      });
      console.log("GTM msg: Accept clicked with cookieconsent_status: " + status);
  }
});
</script>
